{
  "stem": "24195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that somebody might take offense to it and say, why-- you know, what is he doing?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- well, why is he-- why isn't he in the army, or why isn't he working somewhere, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was, you know, kicked out of the school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was doing this job with this person, you know, in the-- in, in this insurance office.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that, boy, really was like just a, a farce.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was just, you know, it was not really a job, and everybody knew it was just pretend.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pretend work, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not no real work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was-- I think, was the reason why she said that, not to-- and, you know-- instigate any attention by-- draw any attention by somebody else, you know, because everybody was so immersed in their own problems with the air raids.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were-- you know, buildings were destroyed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were still burning, and, and many people were killed, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it didn't seem like a good time to bring the-- bring up this issue, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, might take offense to it, you know, and say-- you know, it was just not-- it was just not smart.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- would not-- no, it would not be safe because somebody might start asking questions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we may have a problem answering them, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So coming back to the-- after the-- our apartment was bombed out in November, which was a terrible air raid--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "November 22, 1943 was a saturation air raid where they systematically bombed a whole-- certain quarters of the city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just everything within that-- within those limits were totally destroyed with incendiary-- blockbuster bombs and then incendiary bombs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then everything started burning down.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
